FBIS3-14469 "drnes059_a_94001" FBIS-NES-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Foreign Ministry Official Assassinated LD2803104194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1000 GMT 28 Mar 94 LD2803104194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Security authorities have announced that Touati Belkacem, deputy director of the African section at the Foreign Ministry, was assassinated this morning in front of his home near Bordj El Kifan in the suburbs of the capital. The victim was attacked by three men armed with automatic pistols as he was preparing to leave his house. The same source added that his wife was wounded.
